quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  54,1,Ola lachiweruzo lili pafupi ndipo mwezi wagawanika pakati
  54,2,"Koma iwo akaona chozizwitsa, sakhulupirira ndipo amati, “Ichi sichina ayi koma matsenga ozama.”"
  54,3,Iwo amakana choonadi koma amatsatira zilakolako zawo. Koma chinthu chilichonse chili ndi kumaliza kwake
  54,4,Ndithudi uthenga waperekedwa kale kwa iwo umene uli ndi chenjezo
  54,5,Wodzadzidwa ndi nzeru koma machenjezo ake sawathandiza iwo china chilichonse
  54,6,"Kotero iwe, asiye okha. Patsiku limene woitana adzawaitana kudza ku chinthu choopsa"
  54,7,"Iwo adzadza kumeneko ndi nkhope zogwa pansi, kuchokera kumanda awo monga dzombe louluka ponseponse"
  54,8,"Adzadza mofulumira kwa oitana anthu osakhulupirira adzati, “Ili ndi tsiku lovuta kwambiri.”"
  54,9,"Asanadze iwo, anthu a Nowa adakana kapolo wathu ndipo adati, “Uyu ndi munthu wamisala.” Ndipo iwo adamuthamangitsa iye ndi kumunyoza kwambiri"
  54,10,"Ndipo iye adadandaula kwa Ambuye wake nati, “Ndagonjetsedwa kotero idzani kuti mundithandize.”"
  54,11,"Motero Ife tidatsekula makomo a kumwamba, ndipo mvula idagwa nthawi yomweyo"
  54,12,Ndipo tidatumphutsa a kasupe padziko lapansi kotero madzi onse adakumana monga mwa lamulo lathu
  54,13,Ndipo tidamunyamula iye m’chombo chopangidwandimatabwandichokhomedwandimisomali
  54,14,Chidanyamuka potsogozedwa ndi Ife. Mphotho kwa iye amene adakanidwa
  54,15,Ndithudi tidachisiya icho ngati chizindikiro koma kodi alipo ena amene adzachenjezedwa
  54,16,Kodi chilango changa ndi chenjezo langa zidali zalikulu bwanji
  54,17,Ndithudi talipanga Buku la Korani kukhala losavuta kulidziwa ndi kulikumbukira. Kodi alipo ena amene adzachenjezedwa
  54,18,Anthu a Aad adakana. Kodi chilango changa ndi chenjezo langa zidali zoopsa bwanji
  54,19,Ndithudi Ife tidatumiza mphepo yamkhuntho pa tsiku latsoka losasimbika
  54,20,Kugwetsa anthu ngati kuti adali mathunthu a mitengo ya mgwalangwa yozulidwa
  54,21,Kodi chilango changa ndipo chenjezo langa zidali zoopsa bwanji
  54,22,Ndithudi talipanga Buku la Korani kukhala losavuta kulizindikira ndi kulikumbukira. Kodi alipo ena amene adzachenjezedwa